CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 12, 1955, pg. B24, reads: "Emanons - Members of the Emanons Club discuss final plans for their second annual Boom Diddy Cabaret Ball slated at the Royal Ballroom, Nov. 25. Left to right: Larry Green, Lloyd Mathews, Samuel Johnson, Nathan Brown, Bobby Tate and Robert Ruffin. Members not shown are Louis King and Dr. Henry Heins."
TitMainTitle: Emanons Club members including Larry Green, Lloyd Mathews, Samuel Johnson, Nathan Brown, Bobby Tate, and Robert Ruffin, gathered around table for meeting in Greene Hearth
